Department Ready 2014 Dodge Charger Hardtop
Controls:
R: Wail Siren
T: Yelp Siren
F: Manual Siren
G: Phaser/Priority Siren
Z: Left turn signal
C: Right turn signal
V: Flood Lights
N: Cruise Lights
M: Parking Lights
L: Lights (Highbeam/Lowbeam)
K: 4-way Directional (Left, Right, Center)
J: Staged Lights (Stage 1, 2, 3)
H: Airhorn
P: Parking brake
I: Camera zoom in
O: Camera zoom out
W: Accelerate
A: Left (Drive)
S: Reverse/Brake
D: Right (Drive)
Q: Gear Shift Up
E: Gear Shift Down
LeftShift: Clutch

Radar Controls:
U: Activate
B: Lock Speed
Z: Increase volume
